    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented here is an automotive specimen of the highest caliber. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting a level of preservation that satisfies even the most discerning collector. Every surface reflects meticulous care, and its mechanical integrity is absolute. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a truly pristine example of engineering excellence.",
